COMMUNITY USE — FREE

This software may be used, modified, and deployed at no cost if you are:

  (a) An individual using Krypto for personal or professional projects,
      regardless of whether those projects generate revenue for you
      personally as a sole trader or freelancer;

  (b) An organisation, company, or entity whose annual gross revenue
      for the most recent fiscal year is less than USD $1,000,000; or

  (c) A verified nonprofit organisation (see Nonprofit Exemption below).

Community use includes the right to:
  - Deploy Krypto for your own use or for clients
  - Modify Krypto for your own use
  - Fork Krypto and contribute changes back

Community use does NOT include the right to:
  - Resell or redistribute Krypto as a competing product or service
  - Remove or obscure BowenLabs copyright notices
  - White-label Krypto and represent it as your own product

