COMMERCIAL USE — LICENSE REQUIRED

If you are an organisation, company, or entity whose annual gross revenue
for the most recent fiscal year equals or exceeds USD $1,000,000, you
must obtain a commercial license from BowenLabs before deploying this
software in any production capacity.

To obtain a commercial license, contact: licensing@bowenlabs.io

A commercial license grants:
  - The right to deploy Krypto in production for commercial purposes
  - The right to modify Krypto for internal use
  - Access to priority support (terms negotiated per agreement)

A commercial license does NOT grant:
  - The right to resell or redistribute Krypto as a competing product
  - The right to white-label Krypto and remove BowenLabs attribution
  - The right to sublicense Krypto to third parties

Using this software in production without a required commercial license
is a violation of this license and of BowenLabs's copyright.

