NONPROFIT EXEMPTION

Verified nonprofit organisations are permanently exempt from the
commercial license requirement, regardless of revenue, provided they
maintain verified nonprofit status.

Qualifying organisations include:
  - 501(c)(3) organisations or equivalent tax-exempt status
  - Registered charities and NGOs in any jurisdiction
  - Educational institutions operating as nonprofits

To apply for nonprofit exemption: licensing@bowenlabs.io
Provide documentation of your nonprofit status. Exemption is granted
per organisation and must be updated if your status changes.

Government agencies and for-profit entities with charitable programs
do not qualify for the nonprofit exemption.

